OL,3,CSecond man charged over alleged arson
OL,4,Cat former synagogue
OL,6,FA second man has been charged over an
OL,7,Falleged arson attack at a former
OL,8,Fsynagogue.
OL,10,FDominique Charles-Turner, 31, from
OL,11,FLeyton in east London, was arrested on
OL,12,FTuesday and has now been charged with
OL,13,Farson with intent to endanger life,
OL,14,Fthe Metropolitan Police said.
OL,16,FHe will appear at Westminster
OL,17,FMagistrates' Court later on Thursday.
OL,19,FDamage was caused to gates and a lock
OL,20,Fat the site in Nelson Street,
OL,21,FWhitechapel, at around 5.10am on May 5.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
