OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778775073
OL,3,CSecond man charged over alleged arson
OL,4,Cat former synagogue
OL,6,FThe former synagogue is in the process
OL,7,Fof being bought by a Muslim community
OL,8,Fgroup with plans to convert it to a
OL,9,Fmosque and community centre.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the Crown
OL,12,FProsecution Service said: "We have
OL,13,Fdecided to charge Dominic Charles
OL,14,FTurner with arson with intent to
OL,15,Fendanger life following an attack at a
OL,16,Fformer synagogue in Nelson Street,
OL,17,FTower Hamlets, on May 5 2026.
OL,26,@tD@[OU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
