OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778775073
OL,3,CSecond man charged over alleged arson
OL,4,Cat former synagogue
OL,6,F"Our prosecutors have worked to
OL,7,Festablish that there is sufficient
OL,8,Fevidence to bring this case to court
OL,9,Fand that it is in the public interest
OL,10,Fto pursue criminal proceedings.
OL,12,F"We have worked closely with the
OL,13,FMetropolitan Police's Counter
OL,14,FTerrorism Command as it carried out
OL,15,Fits investigation.
OL,17,F"We remind all concerned that criminal
OL,18,Fproceedings against this defendant are
OL,19,Factive and that he has the right to a
OL,20,Ffair trial.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
