OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1778775073
OL,3,CSecond man charged over alleged arson
OL,4,Cat former synagogue
OL,6,F"It is vital that there should be no
OL,7,Freporting, commentary or sharing of
OL,8,Finformation online which could in any
OL,9,Fway prejudice these proceedings."
OL,11,FMoses Edwards 45, from Wanstead, has
OL,12,Falready been charged with arson with
OL,13,Fintent to endanger life and is next
OL,14,Fdue to appear in court at the Old
OL,15,FBailey on June 5.
OL,17,FA 52-year-old woman who was also
OL,18,Farrested in connection with the blaze
OL,19,Fwas bailed until August.
